1997;;Top of the World;;American;;Sidney J. Furie;;Peter Weller, Dennis Hopper;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Top_of_the_World_(1997_film);;In Las Vegas for a quickie divorce, a just-paroled ex-cop and his wife wander into the Cowboy Country Casino, run by the shady Charles Atlas. They win big, right as the casino is being robbed. The police believe their big win was a staged diversion, and the two of them become suspects. Over the course of the evening and next morning, the two attempt to escape the surrounded casino and prove their innocence, as well as save their marriage.